    "result": {"pageContext":{"frontmatter":{"title":"UI icons","description":"Icons are important aids to the user experience. Employ icons strategically with careful view to sizing, alignment, clearance and color in usage.","tabs":["Library","Design","Usage","Contribute"]},"relativePagePath":"/iconography/ui-icons/usage.mdx","titleType":"append","MdxNode":{"id":"dd4bfd98-fefc-5e71-a0ef-b54646ebbe3d","children":[],"parent":"0fa9575e-5f8b-55ca-bfd1-d062298b0a6b","internal":{"content":"---\ntitle: UI icons\ndescription:\n  Icons are important aids to the user experience. Employ icons strategically\n  with careful view to sizing, alignment, clearance and color in usage.\ntabs: [Library, Design, Usage, Contribute]\n---\n\n<PageDescription>\n\nIconography is highly functional in a user interface. When used wisely, icons\nbecome an elegant yet efficient way to communicate with and help guide a user\nthrough an experience. To maintain this functionality, it's important to reduce\ncognitive load on users by employing icons sparingly and strategically\nthroughout your designs.\n\n</PageDescription>\n\n<AnchorLinks>\n  <AnchorLink>Sizing</AnchorLink>\n  <AnchorLink>Alignment</AnchorLink>\n  <AnchorLink>Clearance</AnchorLink>\n  <AnchorLink>Color</AnchorLink>\n</AnchorLinks>\n\n<Video src=\"/videos/icon-usage.mp4\" poster=\"/images/icon-usage-poster.jpg\" />\n\n## Sizing\n\nIcons have been designed to work best in four sizes: 16px, 20px, 24px, and 32px.\nPlease use icons at their originally produced size. These are provided in SVG\nand Adobe Illustrator files.\n\n<ArtDirection>\n\n![sizing example](../images/sizing-example-comp-mobile.svg)\n![sizing example](../images/sizing-example-comp.svg)\n\n</ArtDirection>\n\n| Icon size                                     | Stroke width | Padding | Live area | Corner radius | Type sizes |\n| --------------------------------------------- | ------------ | ------- | --------- | ------------- | ---------- |\n| 32px                                          | 2px          | 2px     | 28px      | 2px           | —          |\n| 24px                                          | 1.5px        | 1.5px   | 21px      | 1.5px         | —          |\n| <span class=\"footnote__highlight\">20px</span> | 1.25px       | 1.25px  | 17.5px    | 1.25px        | 16pt       |\n| <span class=\"footnote__highlight\">16px</span> | 1px          | 1px     | 14px      | 1px           | 14pt       |\n\n<Caption>\n  <span class=\"footnote__highlight\" />\n  <span class=\"footnote\">\n    16px and 20px icons are optimized to feel balanced when paired with 14pt and\n    16pt IBM Plex. Use 24px and 32px when larger icons are needed.\n  </span>\n</Caption>\n<ArtDirection>\n\n![four standard icon sizes](../images/sizing-alignment-example-comp-mobile.svg)\n![four standard icon sizes](../images/sizing-alignment-example-comp.svg)\n\n</ArtDirection>\n\n<DoDontRow>\n<DoDont caption=\"Do use the correct icon size with IBM Plex.\">\n\n![correct icon sizing](../images/sizing-correct-size-do.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n<DoDont type=\"dont\" caption=\"Don’t alter icon sizes.\">\n\n![incorrect icon sizing](../images/sizing-correct-size-dont.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n</DoDontRow>\n\n<DoDontRow>\n<DoDont caption=\"Do center-align icons when they’re next to text.\">\n\n![correct sizing alignment](../images/sizing-alignment-do.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n<DoDont type=\"dont\" caption=\"Don’t baseline-align icons to the text.\">\n\n![incorrect sizing alignment](../images/sizing-alignment-dont.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n</DoDontRow>\n\n## Alignment\n\nIcons are optically aligned to the center of the icon grid within the boundary\nbox. Centering ensures all icons will be aligned correctly when exported and\nused side-by-side in a line or a row. Visually center an icon where the visual\nweight is heaviest. In some situations, mechanically centering doesn’t work.\n\n![alignment example](../images/alignment-example-comp.svg)\n\n<ArtDirection>\n\n![icons optically centered on grid](../images/alignment-example-comp-visual-center-mobile.svg)\n![icons optically centered on grid](../images/alignment-example-visual-center-comp.svg)\n\n</ArtDirection>\n\n## Clearance\n\nWhen designing icons for touch surfaces, all targets need to be 44px or greater.\nThe icon can be smaller than 44px if padding is added to the touch target with\nCSS to meet the 44px minimum.\n\n<ArtDirection>\n\n![clearance exmaple](../images/clearance-example-comp-mobile.svg)\n![clearance exmaple](../images/clearance-example-comp.svg)\n\n</ArtDirection>\n\n<DoDontRow>\n<DoDont caption=\"Do follow the clearance rule to allow for legibility and an optimal touch experience.\">\n\n![clearance rule](../images/clearance-do.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n<DoDont type=\"dont\" caption=\"Don’t collapse the icon clearance area.\">\n\n![incorrect clearance](../images/clearance-dont.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n</DoDontRow>\n\n## Color\n\nIcons are always a solid, monochromatic color and need to pass the same color\ncontrast ratio as typography (4.5:1). The color of the icon should reflect the\nimportance of the icon’s action which should always be to help guide a user. For\nmore information on color, see Color in UI.\n\n<DoDontRow>\n<DoDont caption=\"Do match your icon color with your text color when pairing them.\">\n\n![color match](../images/color-match-do.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n<DoDont type=\"dont\" caption=\"Don’t use different colors for text and icons.\">\n\n![incorrect color match](../images/color-match-dont.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n</DoDontRow>\n\n<DoDontRow>\n<DoDont caption=\"Do make icons monotone.\">\n\n![color icon](../images/colored-icon-do.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n<DoDont type=\"dont\" caption=\"Don’t use more than one color within an icon.\">\n\n![incorrect color icon](../images/colored-icon-dont.svg)\n\n</DoDont>\n</DoDontRow>\n","type":"Mdx","contentDigest":"4bb23afb7c2b287395a5f169b6d99a9c","owner":"gatsby-plugin-mdx","counter":1698},"frontmatter":{"title":"UI icons","description":"Icons are important aids to the user